<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /><text>返回工作台</text></view><text>排课管理</text></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content"><view class="selector-grid"><view><image src="{{icons.location}}" mode="aspectFit" /><text>浦东校区</text><text>⌄</text></view><view><image src="{{icons.calendar}}" mode="aspectFit" /><text>第29周 07.13–07.19</text><text>⌄</text></view></view><view class="stat-grid"><view><text>▣ 本周课程</text><text>42<text>节</text></text></view><view><text>▤ 待排</text><text>3<text>节</text></text></view><view><text>⚠ 冲突</text><text>2<text>节</text></text></view><view><text>↻ 变更</text><text>5<text>节</text></text></view></view><view class="week-strip"><view class="{{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{days}}" wx:key="date"><text>{{item.week}}</text><text>{{item.date}}</text></view></view><view class="day-heading"><text>07.16 周四 · 共 6 节课</text><text>按时间 ↑</text></view><view class="course-card" wx:for="{{courses}}" wx:key="time"><text class="course-time">{{item.time}}</text><image src="{{item.avatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="course-copy"><text>{{item.name}}</text><text>{{item.coach}}</text><text>⌖ {{item.place}}　♙ {{item.count}}　<text class="{{item.tone}}">● {{item.status}}</text></text></view><view><button bindtap="openCourse">查看</button><button bindtap="changeCourse">调课</button></view></view><view class="alert-row red">⚠ 冲突提醒 <text>2处冲突 ›</text></view><view class="alert-row">▤ 待排班级 <text>3个班级待安排 ›</text></view><view class="quick-card"><view><text>快速操作</text><text>了解更多调课规则 ›</text></view><view><button bindtap="createCourse">▣ 新建单课<text>快速创建单节课程</text></button><button bindtap="changeCourse">Ⅱ 申请停课<text>提交停课申请</text></button><button>▰ 查看PC复杂排课<text>PC端更强大</text></button></view></view><view class="pc-tip">▰ 更复杂的周课表与批量调课，请前往PC端　<text>去PC端 ›</text></view><button class="primary-button" bindtap="createCourse">＋ 新建排课</button><view class="safe-space"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
